{"tid":1996613,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"我買中倍升股 目標賺50萬（*貼100萬倉)","createTime":"2020-05-01T05:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T21:58:12.000Z","uid":158651,"like":14,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"7efd1d4a281c171a892d2f44d3516c037778a4ee","tid":1996613,"uid":158651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T05:43:42.000Z","msg":"講左倍升股先<br />\n我係$56已經買左近期最hit既平安好醫生(下圖你會見到個cost係$73 因為我係轉過倉黎 所以佢個cost係唔準既 信不信由你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vwHM3aR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvwHM3aR.jpg&h=74f8fb76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n亦都係$17買中美股vir (最高峰係上過$75 依家跌到baba聲都仲有$30)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XJgh9QU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXJgh9QU.jpg&h=9cea6561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但細心睇 你會發現有問題<br />\n就係 你會發現我兩隻都係買得好少 每隻得個萬零蚊<br />\n咁何來100萬倉？？<br />\n<br />\nok, 咁我貼左我個倉出黎先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DpXQLfF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDpXQLfF.png&h=0d8842d4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n吊 你又話100萬倉？<br />\nusd 113,870 x 7.8 = hkd 888,186 剩低個10幾萬去左邊？？<br />\n<br />\n答案係 蝕左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明細如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v41esvo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv41esvo.jpg&h=b9d0bd50&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n蝕左10萬（高峰期蝕過20萬）都仲好意思貼上連登獻世？<br />\n係 因為我覺得只不過係短期波幅<br />\n3-5年後target呢個倉淨賺50萬<br />\n<br />\n究竟點樣可以由蝕20萬到淨賺50萬？<br />\n你條木嘴究竟買個d係咩股票？點解有d我聽都未聽過？<br />\n建呢個倉背後理念係乜？<br />\n<br />\n醫飽個肚先 之後再打"},{"pid":"bf682b13dcda1906919f4990abb16ba354697f1a","tid":1996613,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T05:44:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e686c47084a9729f5798e1626c23daf8baf8b0f","t